            . On the 23rd of July, about eight o'clock in the evening, I was in <placeName id="t18310908-84-crimeloc478">St. Giles'</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-84-crimeloc478" type="placeName" value="St. Giles'"></interp>
