                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-84-off476 t18310908-84-crimeloc478"></join>, with my brother Charles - we heard a scuffle behind; I turned, and saw the prisoner with my brother's handkerchief in his hand - I took hold of him, and gave him in charge.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Q. Was any body with me? A. There was another person with him, but it was in his hand.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-84-person764">
